Mother’s Goose Preschool

https://mothersgoose.in

Welcome to Mother’s Goose Preschool

At Mother’s Goose Preschool, we believe that early childhood is the most important stage in a child’s life. Our goal is to provide a safe, nurturing, and inspiring environment where children can grow academically, socially, emotionally, and physically.

We focus on building a strong foundation for lifelong learning through structured activities, creative exploration, and positive interaction.

Our school is dedicated to helping children develop confidence, curiosity, discipline, and kindness, preparing them for the next stage of their educational journey.

Our Mission

Our mission is to nurture every child’s potential by providing a balanced learning environment that supports intellectual, emotional, social, and physical development.

We aim to create a school where children:

Feel safe and valued

Develop confidence and curiosity

Build strong learning habits

Grow into responsible and compassionate individuals

Our Vision

Our vision is to build a future-ready preschool where children are prepared not only for school but also for life.

We strive to:

Provide modern early childhood education

Combine global learning methods with local cultural values

Continuously improve through research and innovation in education

Our Learning Approach

At Mother’s Goose Preschool, we focus on holistic development, not just academic learning.

Our programs emphasize:

Social Development

Children learn how to interact respectfully with teachers and friends, helping them build strong social skills.

Work Habits

We encourage discipline, responsibility, and focus through daily routines and structured activities.

Conceptual Development

We help children understand concepts through interactive and activity-based learning rather than memorization.

Auditory Memory

Activities such as storytelling, rhymes, and listening exercises help develop strong auditory memory.

Visual Memory

Creative learning tools, puzzles, and visual activities strengthen observation and memory skills.

Language Development

We focus strongly on English communication skills while also respecting and encouraging the mother tongue language.

Our Teachers

Our teachers are well-qualified and experienced in early childhood education. They understand the emotional and developmental needs of young children.

At Mother’s Goose Preschool, we follow a simple rule:

Children should always be treated with patience, kindness, and respect.

Our teachers:

Speak to children in a calm and encouraging manner

Give individual attention to every child

Encourage positive behavior and friendships

To maintain high teaching standards, the school provides regular teacher training and mentorship programs.

Why Choose Mother’s Goose Preschool
Inspired by Leading Preschools

Our approach is inspired by top preschools in Bangalore, known for their advanced early childhood education methods.

Experienced Leadership

The founder has experience mentoring students at ABC Academy in Bangalore, bringing valuable educational insights to our school.

Focus on Complete Child Development

We work on academic, emotional, social, and behavioral development, ensuring children grow in every aspect.

Parent Guidance

We believe parents are partners in a child’s development.
We guide parents on:

Positive parenting

Communication with children

Supporting learning at home

Facilities
Safe Campus

CCTV cameras are installed across the campus to ensure the safety of every child.

Green Environment

Our campus is surrounded by greenery, providing a healthy and peaceful atmosphere for learning.

Dedicated Classrooms

Each class has its own classroom and dedicated teacher, allowing better attention and structured learning.

Caretakers

Supportive caretakers are available to help children feel comfortable and safe.

Join Our Learning Community

At Mother’s Goose Preschool, we aim to create a warm, supportive, and inspiring environment where children enjoy learning and growing every day.

We welcome parents who want their children to develop strong values, confidence, and curiosity about the world.


