3. Admissions Page Content
Admissions Open

We welcome children to begin their learning journey at Mother’s Goose Preschool, where education is joyful, engaging, and meaningful.

Our programs are designed to help children develop confidence, communication skills, and curiosity through structured activities and play-based learning.

Age Groups

We offer programs for the following age groups:

Playgroup: 2 – 3 years

Nursery: 3 – 4 years

LKG: 4 – 5 years

UKG: 5 – 6 years

Admission Process

Visit the school campus or contact us.

Fill out the admission form.

Submit required documents.

Confirm admission and begin the learning journey.

Required Documents

Birth Certificate

Passport size photographs

Parent identification details

For admission inquiries, please contact us or visit the school campus.

